high_descs: Turn around, go across room until reach brown chair with magazine on it.  Turn left to face chair.
Pick up magazine off of brown chair.
Turn left, proceed until reach center of table to your left.  Turn left to face table.
Place magazine on table, in front of statue.
anns.task_desc: Move a magazine from a chair to a table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the coffee table, then go right, to the last brown arm chair on your left.
Pick up the book in the left front corner of the brown arm chair.
Turn around and go to the coffee table to your left.
Place the book in the center of the three boxes of tissue, and the cardboard box, on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a book on the table.

high_descs: turn around and move across the room to the brown cushioned chair in the corner near the window, turn to face the chair
pick up the book that is sitting on the chair
turn to the left and move forward and turn left to face the coffee table
put the book on to the coffee table in between the tissue boxes and the cardboard box
anns.task_desc: put a book on the coffee table
